Introduction
==============

django-social-auth-app utilizes django-registration and
django-social-auth and handle all user related actions within
single application. And packs this up into single application.
So you need not do this setup everytime you build a new page.

Desired actions to be handled:
	* user login/logout
	* user detail edit page
	* forgotten password recreation
	* registration
	* optionally use of 3rd party authentication services

NOTE: Intended to use with feincms.

Installation
==============

1. Clone the read-only repo

     git clone git://github.com/vencax/django-social-auth-app.git

2. Install the dependencies via PIP.

     pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Add socialauthapp into your INSTALLED_APPS as well as other dependant apps.

4. Include vxkforum.urls into your root url conf

     url(r'^auth/', include('socialauthapp.urls')),
		
5. You are done


